      "id": "c21e072d",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "int part2Score = 0;\n\nif (checkSequence(answer2a, \"root, left, right\")) part2Score++;\nif (checkSequence(answer2b, \"left, root, right\")) part2Score++;\nif (checkSequence(answer2c, \"left, right, root\")) part2Score++;\n\nSystem.out.println();\nSystem.out.println(\"Part 2 score: \" + part2Score + \" / 3\");",
